data.description: To create mixed charts with PDF::Reuse
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
This module gives you a possibility to create simple and also
    complex graphs with PDF::Reuse. You can mix different graphs within
    the same chart and you can handle different entities with different
    structure and size within the same chart. Also you can add
    interactive functions to the graphs.
